data.description: Amazing opportunity to own a home in the very desirable city of North Hollywood. A spacious three bedroom, two bathroom home tucked away in a great pocket of North Hollywood. The open concept living room and kitchen offers best use of the space and ideal for entertaining. In addition to the three bedrooms theres a bonus room that over looks the pool ideal for an office, guest room, gym. Home has been recently updated with newer kitchen cabinets, quarts countertops, laminate flooring and a fresh coat of paint.  The detached two car garage has been converted to a full studio with kitchen and a full bath (with no permits). A true entertainers backyard with a large pool that was recently re-plastered wrapped by a beutiful flagstone patio. The large driveway offers plenty of parking, and RV access. If that weren't enough the home has two solar panel systems, one fully paid off and the second on lease from Tesla for only $54 a month.
